item.title: Teleport command. watch ! get rwrd:)
item.dc:creator: @davidi2 Davidi2
item.description:
@davidi2 wrote:

if (command.startsWith("Command name here") { /// I dont need credits
if(playerHasItemAmount(995, 10000000) == true) {
if(combatLevel >= 50) {
teleportToX = 3204;
teleportToY = 3204;
deleteItem(995,GetItemSlot(995),10000000);
}
else {
sendMessage("You need combat level 50 to teleport there!");
} else if(playerHasItemAmount(995, 10000000) == false) {
sendMessage("You don't have enough coins to teleport there!")
}
}

If its delta replace sendMessage with sM. and the combat level variable might be different.
